{"tid":399652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[防走資]港股市引用人民幣計價、交易及結算","createTime":"2017-09-14T06:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T02:05:37.000Z","uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c44f4c4c3cca2eda9ab7638d950dab02417608e2","tid":399652,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T06:50:20.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】金融管理局前總裁任志剛認為，本港股市應引用人民幣計價、交易及結算。<br />\n<br />\n任志剛在網誌撰文，題為「國際金融中心地位與貨幣金融穩定」，重申以港幣作為交易媒介，為內地與海外之間的資金活動提供融通是不切實際，因內地及海外投資者均關注利用港元進行交易時，當中所承受的貨幣風險，以及進行貨幣對沖的有效性。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，本港保持貨幣金融穩定所面對的挑戰不斷增加，會局限本港國際金融中心進一步發展，認為需及早思考，不能待危機出現才處理。<br />\n<br />\n任志剛又指，處理這個挑戰的第一步，是除港元外，在股市引用人民幣計價、交易及結算，配合人民幣進一步國際化的中央政策目標，亦有助本港銀行有效地配對人民幣資產及負債。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=235949\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D235949&d=MkPQCrxZ66B5YIE4xhm3PTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=e1567b00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D235949&h=66bb8800\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=235949</a>"},{"pid":"83c4b7c1e7897df2c86baf0977f5c5b9c9bb06c1","tid":399652,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T06:53:14.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"22df7f6632323f56b8d351b6d477fbe5f1c714d2","tid":399652,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T06:54:47.000Z","msg":"同美金脫勾先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"054955a1d51d9596a227d61631863714c141b91a","tid":399652,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T06:55:19.000Z","msg":"如果人仔真係開放的話,馬交d賭場大廳就一早轉哂做人仔枱啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a8625747e2fa27bce26fd3675fff5526e864839","tid":399652,"uid":79919,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T06:55:44.0